name: Spesial Drop Isra Miraj
description:
Isra is a night journey from Mecca, the Grand Mosque, to Baitul Baqdis or the Aqsa Mosque in Palestine. According to the majority of scholars, this journey is a physical and spiritual journey.

While Miraj is the journey of the Prophet Muhammad being raised to the sky until Sidratul Muntaha.

I hope the nft that I live is blessed by the almighty god
